eispiel <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blockquote\"><code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figure\"><code>&lt;figure&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a>). Eine Fußzeile enthält typischerweise Informationen über den Autor der Sektion, die Copyright-Daten oder Links zu verwandten Dokumente.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Hinweis zur Benutzung:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Informationen über den Autor sollten in ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a> Element eingebettet werden, welches wiederum in einem <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> Element stehen kann.</li>\n <li>Das <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> Element ist kein Sektionsinhalt und führt deshalb auch keine neue Sektion in der <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Begrenzung</a> ein.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Inhaltskategorien</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Fließender Inhalt</a>, greifbarer Inhalt.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubter Inhalt</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Fließender Inhalt</a>, jedoch kein <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> oder <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a> Nachfahre.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Tag Auslassung</th>\n   <td>Keine, sowohl das Anfangs- als auch das End-Tag sind erforderlich.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubte Elternelemente</th>\n   <td>Jedes Element, dass <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">fließenden Inhalt</a> erlaubt. Das <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> Element muss kein Nachfahre eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a> oder anderem <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> Element sein.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM Schnittstelle</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element schließt nur <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">globale Attribute</a> ein.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  Hier ein paar Copyright Informationen oder stattdessen Informationen über den <span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"<\">&amp;lt;</span>Artikel<span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\">\">&amp;gt;</span>?\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/sections.html#the-footer-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;footer&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/sections.html#the-footer-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;footer&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.footer","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Andere Sektions-verwandte Elemente: <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>;</li>\n <li class=\"last\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Sektionen und Begrenzungen eines HTML5 Dokuments</a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Übersicht","id":"übersicht"},{"text":"Attribute","id":"attribute"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das HTML <footer> Element repräsentiert eine Fußzeile für den nahestehendsten Sektionsinhalt oder das Sektionsquellen Element (also das nahestehendste Element wie zum Beispiel <article>, <aside>, <nav>, <section>, <blockquote>, <body>, <details>, <fieldset>, <figure> (en-US), <td>). Eine Fußzeile enthält typischerweise Informationen über den Autor der Sektion, die Copyright-Daten oder Links zu verwandten Dokumente.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<footer>","locale":